Date: Sat, 30 May 2026 11:01:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(storefront): pipe shuffle intro + fix content flash
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- IntroLoader: silaS → Salis via pipe rotation animation
  each step: last letter flies to front, rest slide right
  4 rotations total with elastic bounce on arrival
- Fix content flash: page content hidden (opacity:0) until intro complete
- Both animation options preserved via ANIMATION_TYPE constant
- tl.call(onComplete) replaces broken onComplete in set()
